N.Y. Comp. Codes R. & Regs. Tit. 1 ยง 20.13 - Other order

State Regulations

Other order means an order issued by the secretary
pursuant to the Act, which order regulates the handling of milk in a marketing
area other than that defined in this Part. Notes
